Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特会长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:22.24,title,NTP,0,0,0,,[伤痛(可爱的骨头)]\N[景仰之人]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:22.24,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[標題NETA自Carol O'Connell的「Bone By Bone」日版翻譯「愛おしい骨」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们被亚森大人抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能打倒我 就收回要离开的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕拼上性命也要阻止亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我一点也不美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那朵云仿佛亚森大人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人 亚森大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呀 请回一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一动也不动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会把骆驼搞错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在摇啊摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千两箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[千两箱:江户时代能装千两金币的箱子]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝藏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道里面装着什么 还是算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题啦 我只要7成就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光脑袋的cosplayer吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是贫困潦倒的临时演员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是逃亡武士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就应该是贫困潦倒 你们是故意提起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂妮洛 别突然撞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 去柯蒂利亚那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊 这头发像被烧过一样的人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 帮大忙了安倍同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.23,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[NETA自阴阳师安倍晴明]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这里封印着各式各样的TOYS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.07,PS,NTP,0,1500,600,,[刚才那是TOYS?]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万要小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点以为要溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我溺水了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪盗帝国真废柴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准说我们废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不废柴也不可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被亚森抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不废柴也不可怜也没被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小衣没被抛弃过所以不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抛弃是什么感觉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我什么感觉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伤口上撒盐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在刷新着人格的下限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊怪盗帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不对 怪盗帝町?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说怪盗帝村?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 底层
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,底层的底?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:08.80,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[地上的圆盘是家庭用自动清扫机器人Roomba]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 逮捕!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实的被捕了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有抵抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为被小衣击溃了内心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是冷笑话?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好玩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有权保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所说的一切将被作为呈堂证供
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米兰达警告now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 虽然亚森不知道跑哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过抓住了三守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是横滨的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈佛大学跳级毕业IQ1400兆的天才美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明智小衣所率领的G4呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始上镜头的就只有小衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子...饿了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会害羞的噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人叫你过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:25.25,PS,NTP,700,0,150,,[喂 别开玩笑了!  在小看人吗!]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那挺个沉甸甸的大肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明带着邮件来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废校决定?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废校是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说学院要没了噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来福尔摩斯侦探学院要没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院没了我们要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知所措 不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我稍微瘦一点啊 真犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还带了其他邮件来的噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎...这次是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.97,PS,NTP,0,1100,150,,[支票? 股票?]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.43,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[致各位学生]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是学生会长寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长寄来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事呀!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.47,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[再见]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎...只有这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知所措 不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有的噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.86,PS,NTP,0,1200,0,,[别让我们一直急着!]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 还有的话就别磨蹭快拿来你这个凶犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香 阿部 爱智 桌 美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:40.39,PS,NTP,500,0,0,,[后面三个是“CARDFIGHT!! Vanguard”里的角色名]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入白罗学院的通知?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.20,PS,,0,0,0,,[NETA自阿嘉莎·克莉丝蒂创造的比利时侦探赫丘勒·白罗(Hercule Poirot）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玛波学院的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.33,PS,,0,0,0,,[同NETA自阿嘉莎·克莉丝蒂笔下的女侦探珍·玛波（Jane Marple）]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是沃尔夫侦探学院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.42,PS,,0,0,0,,[跟妮洛一样NETA自作家雷克斯·斯托特笔下的侦探尼禄·沃尔夫(Nero Wolfe)]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Blue Moon侦探学院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.04,PS,,0,0,0,,[NETA自影集雙面嬌娃(Moonlighting，日版(こちらブルームーン探偵社)裡面的偵探社]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要去其他学院?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能让我们继续侦探的学业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长尽了全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国啊 一直都想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是美国 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等大家都成为独当一面的侦探时再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日 我们齐心协力解决事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是给福尔摩斯小队的噗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的话就快点给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微学习点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道噗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我还得给暑假回家了的同学送通知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特性猪油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.47,PS,,0,0,0,,[NETA哆啦A梦拿出道具时的画面]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补充完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.58,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[看着就想吐了]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还有就是虽然鎌仓大侦探被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦探博还是会按照预定举行噗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后追加展馆决定建在别的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就变成单纯的空地了噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经...不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么...为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福尔摩斯侦探学院废校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在临近侦探博的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了丢脸丢到全世界这个要素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横滨暂且可以让人安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.77,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[真是活该]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到来了 警察的时代!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是废校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福尔摩斯小队会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说变回普通的女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.03,PS,,0,0,0,,[此句原自1970年代“糖果合唱团（Candies）”的解散宣言]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通是指...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕落到谷底好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小衣作为人来说真是无下限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无下限 无下限
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕落到谷底了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了亚森大人我们变得何等肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 摇啊摇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人景仰啊 景仰你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来! 那不是亚森大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 摇啊摇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人景仰啊 摇啊摇...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你... 你也来这套吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快清醒过来 别逃避现实!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我醒来!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚你们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是逃避现实不是怪盗应该做的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯通利巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人不就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也在逃避现实吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然做了这种事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事以至此 三人一起切腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何解救这个如被针刺一般的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乳头也硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟怎么才能治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案不是很显然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是福尔摩斯小队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为她们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人才会感到有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情才会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的状况 严峻的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是元凶 所以要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打到她们 用来消气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边以前是亨利埃特会长的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农田也是 学院也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁楼也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的梦想不能放弃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也存在实现不了的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买彩券最多只中过300元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外汇投资也被强制斩仓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说连石油也没挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些本来是我的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛不也是在亚森面前什么都做不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么梦想啊 TOYS也根本没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全完了 先不说希腊的国债 孤注一掷地投资孙巴威币也一落千丈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:42.71,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[孫巴威幣(ズンバブエ・ドル)：NETA自辛巴威幣（ジンバブエ・ドル）]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:42.71,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[完了…什么都…]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办呢 请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亨利埃特学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 免除学分吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 饭也随便吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和谁说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 TOYS回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 在逃避现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯蒂利亚 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特会长不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不向她们报仇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TKB的皮鞭无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪盗帝国 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要无视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛克 把你的头发炸成九连环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮洛 把你的帽子塞满石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯蒂利亚 把你的头发变成霸王花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.84,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[霸王花：有一种腐肉的臭味]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫尔克林 想把侦探服变成超短裙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:17.39,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[眼睛变成转圈的花：NETA自“嬉皮笑园(不可思议的教室)”OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 给我振作一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 花儿真适合你 亨利埃特会长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TOYS吗 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒过来 不要逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有亨利埃特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哦 看 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是亨利埃特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹭蹭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花田 花田 大家都幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:22.14,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,花田 花田 花田…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽女神的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特大人没有抛弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快乐乐 快快乐乐 做花环…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特大人马上就要做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这种违和感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 胸口嘈杂作响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.38,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[斯通利巴用刀来测试是否现实的方法NETA自电影“全面启动(Inception)”]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让我从这里醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利… 失去了亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处在绝望的最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 绝不能逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从严峻的现实中逃避是最轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这种情况并非亚森大人所望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利埃特大人会怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会希望你们这么做吗？希望你们选择逃避吗!?
