Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须要成为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优秀的怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为优秀的侦探？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为优秀的侦探？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡着炽热灵魂的小狮子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你们的爪子撕开困难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.43,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们的血也越过障碍…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好闷热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往是个烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.81,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,…描绘未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经在最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不会再比现在更堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 抓住这只手爬上来吧
